# Sidvin Owner Notification Plan

This document outlines the end-to-end notification strategy for the Sidvin Owner. Every activity performed by a team member in the system will trigger a real-time notification with all non-empty fields.

---

## **Section 1: Masters (Database Updates)**

### **1. 🏘️ Property Update**
*Trigger: When a new Property is added or details (Rent, Area, Contact, Fee Status) are changed.*
> *   **Address:** {address}
> *   **Proposed Rent:** {proposedRent}
> *   **Proposed Area:** {proposedArea}
> *   **Floors:** {noOfFloors} / **Frontage:** {frontage}
> *   **Maps Link:** {googleMapsLink}
> *   **Contact:** {contactPersonName} ({mobile})
> *   **Property Fee Status:** {propertyFeeStatus}
> *   **Paper Signing Date:** {propertyFeePaperSigningDate}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **2. 🏷️ Brand Update**
*Trigger: When a new Brand is added or details (Category, Rep, Service Fees) are changed.*
> *   **Brand Name:** {name}
> *   **Company Name:** {companyName}
> *   **Category:** {category}
> *   **Service Fee Agreed:** {serviceFeeAgreed}
> *   **Assigned Rep:** {assignedRep}
> *   **Contact:** {contactPersonName} ({mobile})
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **3. 📁 Company / Category Master Update**
> *   **List:** {Company Master / Category Master}
> *   **New Entry:** {name}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **4. 👥 Sidvin Team Update**
> *   **Staff Name:** {name}
> *   **Designation:** {designation}
> *   **Role:** {role}
> *   **Action By:** {Admin Name}

---

## **Section 2: Proposals (The Deal Pipeline)**

### **5. 📂 Proposal Updated**
*Trigger: Linking a Property/Brand, or editing proposal details.*
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Serial No:** {serialNo}
> *   **Proposal Date:** {proposalDate}
> *   **Proposal Sender:** {proposalSender}
> *   **Brand Remarks:** {brandRemarks}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **6. 📞 Follow Up Done**
*Trigger: Logging a follow-up action.*
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Follow Up Date:** {followUpDate}
> *   **Status:** {status}
> *   **Remarks:** {remarks}
> *   **Next Follow Up Date:** {nextFollowUpDate} {nextFollowUpTime}
> *   **Planned Visit Date:** {plannedVisitDate}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **7. ❌ Proposal Cancelled**
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Cancellation Reason:** {cancelRemarks}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **8. 🗓️ Visit [Scheduled / Completed]**
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Status:** {scheduledDate ? "Scheduled" : "Completed"}
> *   **Date:** {visitDate || scheduledDate}
> *   **Visit Outcome:** {visitOutcome}
> *   **Attendance:** {sidvinAttendees} / {brandAttendees} / {developerAttendees}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **9. 📜 Terms / Agreement Updated**
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Current Stage:** {signingDate ? "Signed ✍️" : "Finalized 📋"}
> *   **Signing Date:** {signingDate}
> *   **Finalization Date:** {finalizationDate}
> *   **Rent Commencement:** {rentCommencementDate}
> *   **Handover Date:** {handoverDate}
> *   **Agreement Registration Date:** {agreementRegistrationDate}
> *   **Planned Store Opening:** {plannedOpeningDate} / **Actual:** {storeOpeningDate}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **10. 🛠️ Technical Specs Finalized**
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **AC:** {ac} / **Electrical Panel:** {electricalPanel}
> *   **Fire Safety:** {fireFightingSystem} / **Flooring:** {flooring}
> *   **Power Load:** {powerLoad} / **DG Backup:** {dgBackup}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

---

## **Section 3: Deposits (Financial Tracking)**

### **11. 💰 Deposit Update**
*Trigger: When a new deposit stage is created or updated.*
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Stage Name:** {stageName}
> *   **Amount Due:** {amount}
> *   **Total Received Amount:** {receivedAmount}
> *   **Latest Receipt Date:** {receiptDate}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **12. 🧾 Receipt Update**
*Trigger: When a new payment/receipt is added to a specific deposit stage.*
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Deposit Stage:** {stageName}
> *   **Receipt Amount:** {receiptAmount}
> *   **Receipt Date:** {receiptDate}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

### **13. 🥇 Success Story / Billed**
*Trigger: Final closing and invoicing.*
> *   **Property:** {propertyAddress}
> *   **Brand:** {brandName}
> *   **Invoice Status:** Billed ✅
> *   **Invoice No:** {invoiceNo}
> *   **Invoice Date:** {invoiceDate}
> *   **Invoice Amount:** {invoiceAmount}
> *   **Log By:** {updatedBy}

---

## **System Implementation Rules**
1.  **Zero-Blank Policy:** Any field that is **not** filled by a team member in the form will **not** appear in the message.
2.  **Traceability:** Every message MUST capture the **Property, Brand, and Team Member** to ensure accountability.
3.  **Real-Time Delivery:** The notification should be triggered immediately upon form submission.
4.  **Order:** The header provides the context (e.g., 📂 Proposal Updated), while the body provides the property/brand and specific data points.
